<H3> <TI>   Fokker 70 To Be Certified in October 1994 </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94WS0196B Paris AIR &amp; COSMOS/AVIATION MAGAZINE INTERNATIONAL 
in French 2 Jan 94 p 14--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> 94WS0196B </F>
<F P=104>  Paris AIR &amp; COSMOS/AVIATION MAGAZINE INTERNATIONAL 
in French 2 Jan 94 p 14--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>



<TEXT>
